This is a collection of Mythtv config files and scripts I use on Mythbuntu 10.04


Install ruby
$ sudo apt-get install ruby

Run install script, this will install some required packages
$ sudo ./install


With the backup script you can copy that to your cron
$ sudo cp backup/backup-system /etc/cron.daily


Finding duplicates utility
$ cd <media area>

Search for duplicate video files
$ finddups -v

Search for duplicate music files
$ finddups -v

Search specific file types
$ finddups avi
